ZH: 我不经意地踩到了地上的香蕉皮。
EN: I accidentally stepped on a banana peel on the ground.

ZH: 他不经意地将书包遗落在教室里。
EN: He carelessly left his backpack behind in the classroom.

ZH: 她不经意地拿错了手机。
EN: She inadvertently took the wrong phone.

ZH: 我不经意地撞到了路边的树。
EN: I unintentionally bumped into a tree on the side of the road.

ZH: 他不经意地让自己的秘密被人知道了。
EN: He accidentally let his secret be known.

ZH: 她不经意地打翻了桌子上的水杯。
EN: She carelessly knocked over the water glass on the table.

